{{Infobox journal | title = Environment and Behavior | cover = Environment and Behavior.tif | editor = Ann Sloan Devlin | discipline = [[Psychology]] | former_names = | abbreviation = Environ. Behav. | publisher = [[Sage Publications]] | country = | frequency = Bimonthly | history = 1969–present | openaccess = | license = | impact = 3.549 | impact-year = 2017 | website = http://www.sagepub.com/journals/Journal200783/title | link1 = http://eab.sagepub.com/content/current | link1-name = Online access | link2 = http://eab.sagepub.com/content/by/year | link2-name = Online archive | JSTOR = | OCLC = 1568065 | LCCN = 73007395 | CODEN = EVBHAF | ISSN = 0013-9165 | eISSN = 1552-390X }} '''''Environment and Behavior''''' is a bimonthly [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] covering the fields of [[environmental psychology]] and [[environmental studies]]. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Ann Sloan Devlin ([[Connecticut College]]). It was established in 1969 and is published by [[Sage Publications]].
